---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Cluttered Cabinet">
  <section class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 pt-16 md:pt-24 pb-20">
    <div class="border-b border-slate-dark pb-8 mb-12">
      <p class="mono-label mb-4">About</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-[44px] md:text-[60px] leading-[1.05] tracking-tight2 text-slate-dark">
        Darpan Ganatra
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] lg:items-start">
      <div class="space-y-6 max-w-2xl">
        <p class="font-sans text-slate-dark text-[18px] md:text-[20px] leading-[1.5]">
          VP of Machine Learning &amp; Generative AI at <span class="emph">Publicis Health</span>, where I lead a team building production agentic systems — clinical reasoning agents, multi-agent orchestrators, analytics agents — deployed across 20+ pharmaceutical brands.
        </p>

        <p class="font-sans text-slate-dark text-[16px] leading-[1.5]">
          Before Publicis I built ML pipelines on Vertex AI at Amyris (biotech), and led data science teams at NBCUniversal and WWE.
        </p>

        <p class="font-sans text-slate-dark text-[16px] leading-[1.5]">
          Outside production work I'm running two independent research threads: <span class="emph">LUMEN</span> (token-free agent dialogue via compressed transformer states) and <span class="emph">representation engineering</span> for controllable LLM personas (targeting NeurIPS).
        </p>

        <p class="font-sans text-slate-dark text-[16px] leading-[1.5]">
          This site gathers experiment logs, architecture notes, and dead ends.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="border-t border-slate-dark pt-6 lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l lg:pl-8 lg:pt-0">
        <p class="mono-label mb-4">Elsewhere</p>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/darpanganatra/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-sans text-[16px] text-slate-dark hover:underline underline-offset-4">
              LinkedIn →
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/cluttered-cabinet" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-sans text-[16px] text-slate-dark hover:underline underline-offset-4">
              GitHub →
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
